title: Graham Hands Down Soak Off Gel Nail Wraps, 100 Count
description: Hands down soak-off gel wraps were designed to be the easiest, most comfortable way to remove soak-off gel polish and acrylic. These wraps are flexible enough to be used on both finger and toe nails and the unique material and easy-press seal creates a non-slip wrap.

title: Creative Nail Shellac,Moonlight & Roses, 0.25 Fluid Ounce
description: A white color coat with a pearly whimmer finish for the CND Shellac System. This chip free, soak off gel polish applies with the ease of polish and wears like a gel for a two week manicure that removes in minutes. Moonlight and Roses gives nails a pale, soft finish and subtle rosy shimmer, infinitely layerable for custom colors and effects. Featuring CND's exclusive UV3 technology.
